query:
SELECT gl.gestorId, u.name as gestor_nome, COUNT(gl.lojaId) as num_lojas
FROM gestor_lojas gl
JOIN users u ON gl.gestorId = u.id
GROUP BY gl.gestorId, u.name
ORDER BY u.name;
